<p>
By accessing or using the Site or any Services, you consent to receiving these emails from us, but have the right to unsubscribe from receiving future emails at any time (see “Opting Out of Receiving Communications from Us” below).
</p>
<p>We will use your taxpayer information for reporting and compliance purposes in connection with any amounts earned by you or payments made to you via the Service. We will use your mailing address and/or bank account information to remit any payments to you in connection with the Services, either by check or wire transfer. 
</p>
<p>
Additionally, we may use personal information that you provide, or that we learn about you to otherwise improve your use of the Site and the Services. We will also use this information to help us quickly and efficiently respond to inquiries and requests, and otherwise enhance our Services offering for our users. 
</p>

