<p>If at any point in time, you are not interested in receiving emails or other announcements from us, you will be able to “opt-out” by clicking on the specified link in any given email communication or by modifying your personal settings on the Site. Please note that you cannot unsubscribe from certain correspondence from us, including messages relating to your Money Pacific account. 
